== Remarks ==
*<br/>The cursor starts off displayed but can be turned off.  Passing SDL_ENABLE displays the cursor and passing SDL_DISABLE hides it. 

The current state of the mouse cursor can be queried by passing SDL_QUERY; either SDL_DISABLE or SDL_ENABLE will be returned.<br/>*

